(127, 30, 'es_builder_private', '				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n				\r\n			<article data-ix="article-151285230032780904" data-clickable="true" class=""><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151285230167739953" data-clickable="true"><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151285230828945736" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285230828945736_content"><p>Add</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285230828945736_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h2>Add</h2><p>Make transitions between values for css properties.</p><p>[js]scene.add( @element, @transitions, @delay );[/js]</p>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 specification" data-ix="column-151285231000972324" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285231000972324_content"><p>Specyfikacja</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285231000972324_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><h3>Specification</h3></header>"></div><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151285308816537387" data-clickable="true"><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285309344713448" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285309344713448_content"><p>Element</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285309344713448_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h3>Element</h3>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285310569330910" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285310569330910_content"><p>Element</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285310569330910_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>It is item which we want to manipulate.</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>object</i></p></div><p>[js]$(.item)[/js]</p>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285311309812802"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 column" data-ix="column-151285313802311814" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285313802311814_content"><p>Transitions</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285313802311814_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h3>Transitions</h3><p>It is set of css values which you want to change with scrolling.</p><p>[js]&nbsp;<br />[<br />&nbsp; [ [ { css_property: css_property_value, ... }, duration, offset ], <br />&nbsp; ... <br />] <br />[/js]</p>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-15128531457521346" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-15128531457521346_content"><p>css_property</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-15128531457521346_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h5>css_property</h5>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285314978271298" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285314978271298_content"><p>css_property</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285314978271298_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>It is css attribute e.g. opacity, transform. Color attribute supports only rgb, rgba</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p></div>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285316383299553"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285316835593692" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285316835593692_content"><p>the_css_property_value</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285316835593692_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h5>css_property_value</h5>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285317179134847" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285317179134847_content"><p>the_css_property_value</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285317179134847_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>It is css attribute value. Takes from to value.</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p></div>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285317503122808"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285318062082976" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285318062082976_content"><p>Duration</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285318062082976_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h5>Duration</h5>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285318381067052" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285318381067052_content"><p>Duration</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285318381067052_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>Duration of transition.</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>integer </i><i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p><p>Integer <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>0.1 = 100</i><br />String <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>100 = 100</i><br />String <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>50% = 50%</i></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;of scene</p></div>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285318504068017"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285318744223594" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285318744223594_content"><p>Offset</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285318744223594_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h5>Offset</h5>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-15128531903236547" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-15128531903236547_content"><p>Offset</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-15128531903236547_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>Offset of transition. The offset is added to previous transition offset.</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>integer </i><i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p><p>Integer <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>0.1 = 100</i><br />String <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>100 = 100</i><br />String <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>50% = 50% </i><br />&nbsp; of scene</p></div>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285322678039610"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285322976672077" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285322976672077_content"><p>Delay</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285322976672077_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h3>Delay</h3>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285323275744969" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285323275744969_content"><p>Delay</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285323275744969_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>Delay between next item. If element has length &amp;gt; 1 then you can add delay between next item transitions</p></header><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p></div><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Default <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>0</i></p></div><p>&nbsp; E.g. +0.1</p>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285323663776996"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151285323944985261" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285323944985261_content"><p>Example</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285323944985261_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h2>Examples</h2><p>[js] scene.add( $(''.element''), [</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[{ opacity: [0,1], color: rgb([0,255],[0,255],[0,255]) }, 0.2, 0],</p><p>]);[/js]</p><p>[js] scene.add( $(''.element''), [</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[{ opacity: [0,1] }, 0.2, 0],</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[{ transform: rotate([0,360]deg) }, 0.2, 0.1], // ( Auto offset =&amp;gt; prev offset + prev duration + this offset )</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[{ transform: translateX([0,100)px) translateY([0,100]px), opacity: [1,0] }, 0.2, 0], // ( Auto offset =&amp;gt; prev offset + prev duration + this offset )</p><p>]);[/js]</p>"></div></div></div></div></div></article>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			<article data-ix="article-151285530428413357" data-clickable="true" class=""><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151285530733340936" data-clickable="true"><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151285531337835756" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285531337835756_content"><p>pin</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285531337835756_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h2>Pin</h2><p>Create pinning. Using timeline sytem you can create multi pins.</p><p>[js]&nbsp;scene.pin( @element, @timeline ); [/js]</p>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 specification" data-ix="column-151285559723074563" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285559723074563_content"><p>Specyfikacja</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285559723074563_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><h3>Specification</h3></header>"></div><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151285562698322203" data-clickable="true"><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285565485312829" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285565485312829_content"><p>Element</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285565485312829_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h3>Element</h3>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151285565968493324" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285565968493324_content"><p>Treść edytora</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285565968493324_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<header><p>It is item which you want to pin.</p></header><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>object</i></p></div><p>[js]$(.item)[/js]</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285566100250158"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151285566410628983" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285566410628983_content"><p>Timeline</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285566410628983_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h3>Timeline</h3>"></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5" data-ix="column-151285566733917234" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285566733917234_content"><p>Treść edytora</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285566733917234_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<p>It is set of another sets which contains values of pin.</p><p>Each set in a @timeline is called pin. For better understanding.</p><p>[js][ // start timeline</p><p>[ duration, offset, @variable ], // pin</p><p>[ duration, offset, @variable ],&nbsp;// pin</p><p>....</p><p>][/js]</p><p>Every pin has&nbsp;<i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>Auto offset =&amp;gt; prev pin''s offset + prev pin''s duration + that pin offset</i></p><h5>&nbsp;</h5><h5>@Vartiable</h5><div class=&quot;row&quot;><p>Type <i class=&quot;lighting&quot;>string</i></p></div><p>It is variable which contains parameters of the pin from timeline. You can get the set of the parameters by <strong>var function</strong>.</p>"></div></div><div class="clear" data-clickable="true" data-ix="clear-151285668999251768"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 checked" data-ix="column-151285669361132855" data-clickable="true">col-xsmall-8 <div class="editable_item no-margins" data-ix="column-151285669361132855_content"><p>Example</p><input name="column-content-editor" id="column-content-editor" type="text" data-ix="column-151285669361132855_hidden" hidden="hidden" value="<h2>Example</h2><p>[js] var timeline = [</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[ 0.4, 0],</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[ 0.35, 0, ″second-pin″],</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;[ 0.35, 0.2 ]</p><p>];</p><p>scene.pin( $(element), timeline );[/js]</p>"></div></div></div></div></div></article>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			\r\n			'),
