(261, 30, 'es_builder_output', 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:4:"cols";s:8:"children";a:1:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:13:"col-xsmall-8 ";s:7:"content";s:466:"<h2>Add</h2><p>Make transitions between values for css properties.</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript">scene<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">add</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> @element<span class="token punctuation">,</span> @transitions<span class="token punctuation">,</span> @delay <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre>";}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"cols specification";s:8:"children";a:21:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"col-xsmall-8 title";s:7:"content";s:57:"<p> </p><header><h3>Specification</h3></header><p> </p>";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:16:"<h3>Element</h3>";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:372:"<header><p>It is item which we want to manipulate.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">object</i></p></div><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>item<span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre>";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"col-xsmall-8 break";s:7:"content";s:245:"<h3>Transitions</h3><p>It is set of css values which you want to change with scrolling.</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class=" language-html">[ [ [ { css_property: css_property_value, … }, duration, offset, variable ], … ]</code></pre>";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:30:"<h5><em>css_property</em></h5>";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:174:"<header><p>It is css attribute e.g. opacity, transform. Color attribute supports only rgb, rgba</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">string</i></p></div>";}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:36:"<h5><em>css_property_value</em></h5>";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:137:"<header><p>It is css attribute value. Takes from to value.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">string</i></p></div>";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:11;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:26:"<h5><em>Duration</em></h5>";}i:12;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:400:"<header><p>Duration of transition.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">integer </i><i class="lighting">string</i></p></div><div class="row"><p> </p><div class="row"><p>Integer <i class="lighting">0.1 = 100</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>String <i class="lighting">100 = 100</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>String <i class="lighting">50% = 50%</i>of scene</p></div></div>";}i:13;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:14;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:24:"<h5><em>Offset</em></h5>";}i:15;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:426:"<header><p>Offset of transition. The offset is added to previous transition offset.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">integer </i><i class="lighting">string</i></p></div><div class="row"><p> </p><p>Integer <i class="lighting">0.1 = 100</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>String <i class="lighting">100 = 100</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>String <i class="lighting">50% = 50%</i>of scene</p></div>";}i:16;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:17;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:23:"<h3><em>Delay</em></h3>";}i:18;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:376:"<header><p>Delay between next item. If exist more than 1 element found using class or other property then you can add delay between next item transitions.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">string</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Default <i class="lighting">0</i></p></div><pre class=" language-html"><code class=" language-html">E.g. +0.1</code></pre>";}i:19;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:20;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:13:"col-xsmall-8 ";s:7:"content";s:5500:"<h3>Examples</h3><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript">scene<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">add</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>‚<span class="token punctuation">.</span>element’<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>\n    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> opacity<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> color<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">rgb</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">255</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">255</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">255</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0.2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript">scene<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">add</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>‚<span class="token punctuation">.</span>element’<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>\n    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> opacity<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0.2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>\n    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> transform<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">rotate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">360</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>deg<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0.2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0.1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment">// ( Auto offset =&gt; prev offset + prev duration + this offset )</span>\n    <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> transform<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">translateX</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">100</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>px<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token function">translateY</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">100</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>px<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> opacity<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0.2</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment"