(1000003, 26, 'es_builder_output_backup', 'a:1:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:4:"cols";s:8:"children";a:1:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:13:"col-xsmall-8 ";s:7:"content";s:664:"<h2>Description</h2><p>Trigger calls events during scrolling on scene. The element contains 2 attributes. Name and margin top. You have to create trigger and add to enedScroll function. It should looks like example below.</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">var</span> trigger <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">enedScroll<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Trigger</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> @name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> @marginTop <span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre>";}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"cols specification";s:8:"children";a:6:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"col-xsmall-8 title";s:7:"content";s:39:"<header><h3>Specification</h3></header>";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:13:"<h3>Name</h3>";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:190:"<header><p>Shows the name above the trigger.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">string</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Default <i class="lighting">null</i></p></div>";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:19:"<h3>Margin top</h3>";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 ";s:7:"content";s:208:"<header><p>Margin from top allowing adjust moment of call event.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">integer</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Default <i class="lighting">0</i></p></div>";}}}}}'),
(1000004, 28, 'es_builder_output_backup', 'a:1:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:4:"cols";s:8:"children";a:1:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:13:"col-xsmall-8 ";s:7:"content";s:921:"<h2>Description</h2><p>The function create new scene and it is preparing container of functions which allow you to create actions. The function is connecting all values, target as scene, trigger, selectors and visual. You can use the function by following the example below.</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">var</span> scene <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">enedScroll</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> @target <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> @trigger <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> @options <span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre>";}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"cols specification";s:8:"children";a:11:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:18:"col-xsmall-8 title";s:7:"content";s:57:"<p> </p><header><h3>Specification</h3></header><p> </p>";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:15:"<h3>Target</h3>";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:757:"<header><p>It is element which is the point of reference for offset and duration. All these values ​​will be suggesting by the target’s properties. E.g. Integer 0 for offset means offset of the target. Above it is described as scene.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">string </i><i class="lighting">object</i></p></div><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>my<span class="token operator">-</span>item<span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token punctuation">.</span>my<span class="token operator">-</span>item</code></pre>";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:16:"<h3>Trigger</h3>";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:516:"<header><p>Here you add trigger, easiest way is by variable. Read about trigger. If is empty then enedScroll create default trigger with margin top equals 0.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">object</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Default <i class="lighting">0</i></p></div><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">enedScroll<span class="token punctuation">.</span>Trigger</span></code></pre>";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:25:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-3 ";s:7:"content";s:16:"<h3>Options</h3>";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:30:"col-xsmall-8 col-small-5 break";s:7:"content";s:455:"<header><p>It consists of two keys, selectors and visual. Read about selectors Read about visual.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">object</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Selectors default <i class="lighting">[0,0]</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Visual default <i class="lighting">{ }</i></p></div><pre class=" language-html"><code class=" language-html">{ selectors: @selectors_options, visual: @visual_options }</code></pre>";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:5:"class";s:5:"clear";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:5:"class";s:13:"col-xsmall-8 ";s:7:"content";s:1074:"<h2>Example</h2><p>Full build of function</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class=" language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">enedScroll</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>‚<span class="token punctuation">.</span>element’<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> trigger<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> selectors<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> visual<span class="token punctuation">:</span> visual_defaults <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><p>Where trigger and visual_defaults are variables.</p>";}}}}}'),
