(24, 1, '2017-11-24 23:31:48', '2017-11-24 22:31:48', '<article data-ix="article-15126757347714447"><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151267573765915900"><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151267575169479482"><div data-ix="column-151267575169479482_item" editor-item=""><h2 class="title">Selectors</h2><p>Top and bottom selector can moving by manipulate value in object which you can join with enedScroll function.</p></div></div><div class="clear" data-ix="clear-151267577709930180"></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 specification" data-ix="column-151267576052518393"><div class="cols" data-ix="row-151267580148776111"><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151267754640954830"><div data-ix="column-151267754640954830_item" editor-item=""><header><h3>Specification</h3></header></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-3" data-ix="column-151267583368757893"><div data-ix="column-151267583368757893_item" editor-item=""><h3>Description</h3></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8 col-medium-5 column" data-ix="column-151267585575882330"><div data-ix="column-151267585575882330_item" editor-item=""><header><p>Contains 2 values which are used. Value with key bigger than 1 is ignored.</p></header><div class="row"><p>Type <i class="lighting">object</i></p></div><div class="row"><p>Default <i class="lighting">[0,0]</i></p></div></div></div><div class="col-xsmall-8" data-ix="column-151267596220190084"><div data-ix="column-151267596220190084_item" editor-item=""><h3>Examples</h3><p><img src="http://localhost/enedScroll%20-%20build/docs/index.php/orginal/selectors_example_1.png" alt="selectors example 1"></p><p><img src="http://localhost/enedScroll%20-%20build/docs/index.php/orginal/selectors_example_2.png" alt="selectors example 2"></p><p><img src="http://localhost/enedScroll%20-%20build/docs/index.php/orginal/selectors_example_3.png" alt="selectors example 3"></p></div></div></div></div></div></article><article data-ix="article-151267573493849688"><div class="cols" data-ix="row-15